    "description": "The Dolphin DCI 1.2 is a PCI-card that provides a standard definition/high definition serial digital interface. This is a Doremi decoder hardware card that contains a JPEG-2000 decoder hardware and BNC serial digital interface connectors used in Doremi Digital Cinema Servers like the DCP-2000. The Dolphin DCI 1.2 utilizes a dual-link encoded serial digital interface for output of DCI compliant resolutions up to 2040x1080p24 (2K-film). It can also operate single link for lower resolution material (i.e. trailers, advertisement, etc.).",
